          25th November is marked as the International Day for the Elimination
          of Violence against Women. The UN makes efforts to raise awareness
          about the women around the world who are victims of gender based
          violence. <br> Sakhya organized various awareness programmes including
          distribution of leaflets, talks, sessions, competitions, street play
          and rally in strategic places
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- img carousal 1 heading -->
